description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have a variety of Bank Cleaning Operative positions available. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We will be happy to discuss these availabilities with you at interview. Or you can call us now to discuss. 01904 725227 or 01904 725516. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a post based within our York Teaching Hospital Facilities Management team? Are you a strong team player, friendly and motivated? Then we may have the role for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;York Teaching Hospital Facilities Management are looking for friendly, approachable and flexible Cleaning Operatives who are excellent communicators, hardworking and can work on their own initiative and also within a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your day-to-day activities will include general cleaning duties such as dusting, vacuuming, mopping, cleaning of patient bed areas, sanitary fittings and empty waste bins. Cleaning will be in areas such as wards, departments and general areas. You will need to complete relevant checklists and other paperwork related to the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So what are your benefits?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive hourly rate (+ 12.07% in lieu of holidays) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhanced Pay for unsocial hours worked&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DBS and Uniforms provided free of charge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fantastic discounts for staff, including local restaurants and shops&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidates will be professional, conscientious, committed, have a good understanding of both written and spoken English and have a ‘can do’ attitude.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to receiving your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emily Bousfield&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Domestic Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emily.Bousfield@YTHFM.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01904725227&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Domestic Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Domestic.Services@York.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01904 725516&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please do call us so we can discus our various shifts with you&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;York Teaching Hospital Facilities Management LLP (YTHFM LLP) provides a full range of estates and facilities services to York Teaching Hospital NHS Foundation Trust, together with project management for capital investments. YTHFM LLP is a partnership between York Teaching Hospital NHS Foundation Trust and Northumbria Healthcare Facilities Management Limited.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New starters will be employed by YTHFM and not directly by the NHS, however, they will enjoy the same terms and conditions as NHS staff covered by Agenda for Change. YTHFM employees have access to the NHS pension scheme.&lt;/p&gt;
